    {
      "risk": "Provider rate limiting — Twilio or SendGrid throttles requests during peak delivery windows",
      "severity": "medium",
      "mitigation": "The queue naturally provides backpressure. Configure worker concurrency to stay within provider rate limits. Add per-provider rate limiting in dispatchers if needed."
