      "risk": "Team unfamiliarity with async patterns leading to debugging difficulty",
      "severity": "low",
      "mitigation": "Include a correlationId (= eventId) in all log entries across all components. Use structured logging. This makes tracing an event from publish to dispatch a single log query."
    }
  ],

